Dialogue: 100,0:00:28.80,0:00:29.51,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}管他呢\N{\fnArial\fs48}Whatever.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:33.75,0:00:34.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}让我走吧！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ah! Let me go!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:35.82,0:00:36.97,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}够了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Enough of this.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:39.35,0:00:40.55,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你想要我什么？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What do you want from me?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:40.55,0:00:44.26,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我想离开这个讨厌的宝石抛弃了的星球\N{\fnArial\fs48}I want to get off this lousy gem-forsaken planet.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:45.91,0:00:47.35,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你一定得修好这个！\N{\fnArial\fs48}You have to fix this.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:47.48,0:00:48.42,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}等等，什么？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Wait, what?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:48.71,0:00:52.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你是我最后的机会了，我没有烧瓶机器人了\N{\fnArial\fs48}You're my last chance. I've got no flask robonoids.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:52.06,0:00:53.42,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我也没有脚了\N{\fnArial\fs48}I've got no foot.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:53.42,0:00:55.66,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我到现在还没收到黄钻石的回应\N{\fnArial\fs48}I've got no response from yellow diamond.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:57.33,0:00:59.60,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我知道你修复了青金石的宝石\N{\fnArial\fs48}I know you fixed Lazuli's gem.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:59.88,0:01:02.57,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不论你做什么，你一定得对通往母世界的传送台照做\N{\fnArial\fs48}Whatever you did, you've got to do it to the homeworld warp.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:02.71,0:01:03.91,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}否则！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Or else!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:04.51,0:01:06.84,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃，好的，只要-只要给我一点时间\N{\fnArial\fs48}Uh, okay. Just -- just give me a second.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:07.15,0:01:09.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我受惊吓时嘴会变得很干\N{\fnArial\fs48}My mouth gets really dry when I'm scared.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:11.33,0:01:12.17,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}来吧\N{\fnArial\fs48}Here goes.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:15.97,0:01:18.99,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那是什么？一点效果都没有啊！\N{\fnArial\fs48}What was that? It didn't do anything!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:19.28,0:01:21.02,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这并不总是起作用\N{\fnArial\fs48}It doesn't always work.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:21.31,0:01:21.75,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不\N{\fnArial\fs48}No.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:22.20,0:01:24.93,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不不不不不！这一定得起作用啊！\N{\fnArial\fs48}No, no, no, no, no! It has to work!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:25.31,0:01:26.60,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我实在抱歉\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:31.80,0:01:34.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}就这样吧，我的最后的尝试\N{\fnArial\fs48}This was it. This was my last shot.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:35.46,0:01:36.33,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我会死在这里的\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm gonna die here.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:36.57,0:01:37.64,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ohhh.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:37.64,0:01:40.77,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嘿，嘿，别啊，地球也没那么遭\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hey, hey, come on. Earth isn't that bad.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:41.00,0:01:42.77,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}地球怎么样无所谓\N{\fnArial\fs48}It doesn't matter what earth is like.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:42.97,0:01:45.12,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}反正不久之后就没样子了\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's not going to be like anything soon.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:45.44,0:01:46.48,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你是指？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:49.64,0:01:50.79,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}他在那！\N{\fnArial\fs48}There he is.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:51.11,0:01:51.66,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}各位！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Guys!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:51.91,0:01:54.26,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}发生了什么？噢，你没事就好！\N{\fnArial\fs48}What happened? Oh, you're okay!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:54.35,0:01:54.93,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}橄榄石！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Peridot!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:55.66,0:01:57.84,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}为什么你们就不能离我远点！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Why can't you just leave me alone?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:58.04,0:01:59.11,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}宝石人们，上！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Gems, move!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:05.57,0:02:05.91,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哈！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ha!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:08.28,0:02:09.54,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这次可别想了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Not this time.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:16.48,0:02:19.15,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}等等，等等，你-你们需要我\N{\fnArial\fs48}Wait, wait. You -- you need me.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:19.15,0:02:21.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我是唯一一个知道-\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm the only one who knows about the --
Dialogue: 100,0:02:29.35,0:02:30.66,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}什么鬼东西？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What on earth?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:31.02,0:02:34.16,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃，真恶心，她的碎片掉了一地\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ugh, sick. There's bits of her all over.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:34.37,0:02:36.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不，她在这里\N{\fnArial\fs48}Nope. She's right here.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:36.82,0:02:37.94,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}现在她在庙里了\N{\fnArial\fs48}And now she's in the temple.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:38.75,0:02:41.55,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那么，这些并不算她身体的一部分？\N{\fnArial\fs48}So, these weren't actually part of her body?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:41.71,0:02:43.20,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃，哎呀\N{\fnArial\fs48}Uh, whoops.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:44.37,0:02:46.84,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}石榴，她刚才试图告诉我们什么\N{\fnArial\fs48}Garnet, she was trying to tell us something.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:47.37,0:02:50.13,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那只是被抓住的宝石人的绝望挣扎\N{\fnArial\fs48}Those are just the desperate lies of a gem who's been caught.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:50.60,0:02:52.52,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你不用再担心她了\N{\fnArial\fs48}You don't need to worry about her anymore.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:52.93,0:02:54.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}来吧，史蒂文\N{\fnArial\fs48}Come on, Steven.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:54.40,0:02:56.31,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，我很高兴这总算结束了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, I'm so glad this is finally over.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:02.06,0:03:04.71,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我回来绑架你了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm back to kidnap you!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:04.97,0:03:05.53,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}怎么？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:06.08,0:03:08.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}过了这么久现在已经能用来开玩笑了，对吧？\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's been long enough that we can joke about it, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:08.46,0:03:09.73,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}才过了大概一小时吧\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's only been like an hour.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:10.26,0:03:12.75,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那么，呃，你拿着她的脚干嘛？\N{\fnArial\fs48}So, ew, what are you doing with her foot?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:13.80,0:03:14.66,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}觉得能带来好运吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Think it's lucky?
Dialogue: 600,0:03:13.80,0:03:14.66,Hint,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,50)}在某些文化中兔子的脚能带来好运
Dialogue: 100,0:03:14.97,0:03:16.00,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}橄榄石可无福消受\N{\fnArial\fs48}Not for Peridot.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:18.53,0:03:20.55,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那么，很高兴你回来\N{\fnArial\fs48}Well, glad to have you back.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:21.20,0:03:22.73,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃...紫晶？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Um...Amethyst?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:23.26,0:03:24.11,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}怎么？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yeah?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:24.42,0:03:25.68,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃...你觉得...\N{\fnArial\fs48}Uh...Do you think...
Dialogue: 100,0:03:27.24,0:03:29.25,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}没什么，别在意\N{\fnArial\fs48}No, it's okay. Never mind.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:30.55,0:03:31.77,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}好吧，怪胎\N{\fnArial\fs48}Okay, weirdo.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:32.13,0:03:34.68,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}如果你需要任何东西，我一直在我的房间-吃垃圾\N{\fnArial\fs48}If you need anything, I'll be in my room eating garbage.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:34.88,0:03:35.31,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}好的\N{\fnArial\fs48}Okay.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:43.08,0:03:46.24,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}为什么你那么害怕？你本要说什么？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Why were you so scared? What were you going to say?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:46.82,0:03:50.04,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}现在你被困在神庙深处的泡泡里，而我们也永远不会知道了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Now you're deep in the temple in a bubble and we'll never know.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:50.53,0:03:52.53,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}如果我有机会和你再多交流一秒...\N{\fnArial\fs48}If I could just talk to you for one more second...
Dialogue: 100,0:03:58.86,0:04:01.00,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}房间，我要和橄榄石谈话\N{\fnArial\fs48}Room, I need to talk to Peridot.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:01.91,0:04:03.77,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我是唯一一个知道-\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm the only one who knows about the --
Dialogue: 100,0:04:06.40,0:04:07.35,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}什么啊？\N{\fnArial\fs48}the what?!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:08.55,0:04:10.33,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃，不不不\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ugh. No, no, no.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:10.71,0:04:12.64,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}房间，我要去地下室\N{\fnArial\fs48}Room, I need to go to the basement.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:12.88,0:04:13.84,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}真正的地下室\N{\fnArial\fs48}The real basement.
